action(Map) - Method in class org.labProject.Agents.Courier
The behavior of this agent goes as follows:
If there is enough product in MobHeadquarters, the Courier simply waits around If there is a need to resupply, the Courier goes to the Plantation If the plantation has enough product, Courier stocks up and returns to MobHeadquarters If there is not enough product, Courier waits until there is, and resumes his actions
action(Map) - Method in class org.labProject.Agents.Dealer
The behavior of this agent goes as follows:
If the time is right Dealer goes out selling drugs. If the Dealer has no drugs in his inventory, he goes to MobHeadquarters If there is enough drugs in the MobHeadquarters he stocks up on them and goes selling. If there is not enough drugs, Dealer waits until there is, and resumes his actions
